clucky
Homonym Number:
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number:
Definition:wanting a child; of a woman: pregnant; broody. [1941 Baker.] Acting as if one yearned for babies, grandchildren, also cluckiness.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
